headline: CoreSite Expands Silicon Valley Campus with Completion of 228,000-Square-Foot, AI-Ready Data Center
summary: DENVER, July 30, 2025--CoreSite, an American Tower company (NYSE: AMT) empowering critical business and AI workloads that impact everyday life through interconnected data center solutions, today announced the completion of a major expansion at its Silicon Valley campus.
